name: Facebook Timeline Cover Photo
description: Choose from various designs to show off your Beck McCormick Photography photo(s). Please view the Facebook Timeline Cover Photo album to see samples to choose from: Click here for album! Your Facebook Timeline Cover Photo will be delivered via e-mail, following your approval of the proof. Simply upload, and wait for the comments and likes to roll in! Please contact Beck to specify which option you would like immediately after purchase. E-mail: beckmccormickphotography@gmail.com. *Note* -- some Timeline Cover Photos are able to be modified slightly, such as text options. Beck McCormick Photography's watermark on your Cover Photo is not optional.
